e":"2017-08-09T14:48:04.000Z","msg":"大學個陣生過，又係壓力大<br />\n好快無事"},{"pid":"e9706bcc11ccb4fb108cac53a8bdde24d920594a","tid":353393,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電話台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇健康台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea650e416ad5b2535144e4db48f962a0037bc84","tid":353393,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"畢業岩岩出黎做野又係壓力大生過<br />\n即時睇醫生好快冇事<br />\n好多病都年輕化"},{"pid":"902b8551cf6c258019329e26c327c257b1619df9","tid":353393,"uid":134623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:10:20.000Z","msg":"識人廿頭生過 半年唔夠驗到cancer<br />\n<br />\n巴打小心"},{"pid":"1a56d5bae4a563d3794c5eb398a72d9393430222","tid":353393,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畢業岩岩出黎做野又係壓力大生過<br />\n即時睇醫生好快冇事<br />\n好多病都年輕化</blockquote><br />\nSame as me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ea8022bae03dcd580efa032958d98624a732c8","tid":353393,"uid":102225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人廿頭生過 半年唔夠驗到cancer<br />\n<br />\n巴打小心</blockquote><br />\n佢點樣發現cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852405b1f003447bc732fef65506dc6760323205","tid":353393,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"ce al 大學final前生過<br />\n醫生話我壓力大＋夜訓 ＝＞皮膚免疫系統gg＝＞生蛇<br />\n話唔搞佢都會2個禮拜內自動冇事<br />\n但都比左藥膏我搽，止痛，快d好番<br />\n同埋佢話生得一次以後<br />\n免疫系統再搞唔掂既話會同一個位置生<br />\n<br />\n利伸：生响眼內角"},{"pid":"8b83fb52dbb4810f58d95f2506e2f6a6a0adacb7","tid":353393,"uid":134623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識人廿頭生過 半年唔夠驗到cancer<br />\